data.description: Great location in quiet neighborhood 2.4 miles from L3Harris and less and 2 miles from shopping and restaurants!  Home has BRAND NEW ROOF W TRANSFERABLE WARRANTY, NEW CARPET, FRESH PAINT and is move-in ready!  Kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and the refrigerator conveys with sale.  Great floor plan with high ceilings and lots of natural light.  Spacious closes throughout and ensuite bath in master bedroom complete with walk-in closet.  Backyard has covered patio, 8'x10' shed, and 24' diameter aboveground pool - perfect for getting out of the Texas heat!
